# ETUS Workflow — Phases, Outputs & Destinations

**Repository destination:** everything under `/docs` with phase subfolders.

---

## Phases → Outputs → Destination

| Phase          | Output (file)                                                                                              | Owner        | Destination                  |
| -------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------ | ---------------------------- |
| Analysis       | `product-brief.md`                                                                                         | Analyst/PM   | `docs/analysis/briefs/`      |
| Analysis       | `brainstorming-output.md`                                                                                  | Facilitator  | `docs/analysis/brainstorms/` |
| Analysis       | `market-research.md`                                                                                       | Analyst      | `docs/analysis/research/`    |
| Analysis       | `competitor-analysis.md`                                                                                   | Analyst      | `docs/analysis/research/`    |
| Planning       | `prd.md`                                                                                                   | PM           | `docs/planning/`             |
| Planning       | `epics.md`                                                                                                 | PM           | `docs/planning/`             |
| Planning       | `user-stories.md`                                                                                          | PM           | `docs/planning/`             |
| Solutioning    | `story/US-###.md`                                                                                          | Dev/QA       | `docs/solutioning/stories/`  |
| Solutioning    | `frd.md`                                                                                                   | PM/Eng       | `docs/solutioning/`          |
| Implementation | `srs.md`                                                                                                   | Eng          | `docs/implementation/`       |
| Implementation | `architecture-diagram.md`                                                                                  | Arch         | `docs/implementation/`       |
| Implementation | `tech-spec.md`                                                                                             | Eng          | `docs/implementation/`       |
| Implementation | `backend-requirements.md`                                                                                  | BE           | `docs/implementation/`       |
| Implementation | `frontend-requirements.md`                                                                                 | FE           | `docs/implementation/`       |
| Data           | `drd.md`, `dbrd.md`, `data-flow-diagram.md`, `data-dictionary.md`, `database-schema.md`, `data-catalog.md` | Data         | `docs/data/`                 |
| UX             | `uxsm.md`, `wireframes.md`, `uxdd.md`, `design-requirements.md`, `style-guide.md`                          | UX           | `docs/ux/`                   |
| Meta           | `checklists.md`, `workflow.md`, `README.md`                                                                | Orchestrator | `docs/meta/`                 |

## Orchestration (roles)

- **Analyst/PM/Architect** conduzem _Analysis & Planning_;
- **Scrum/Dev/QA** conduzem _Solutioning & Implementation_;
- **Data/UX** cruzam as fases conforme artefatos.

## Hand‑offs (by ID)

- Vision → JTBD/Journey → BRD → **PRD‑F** → Epics → US → FR → **SRS** → Arch/Tech → FE/BE/Data/UX.

## Rules (No‑Overlap)

- Aceitação só em **User Stories**; NFRs numéricos só no **SRS**; tokens só no **Style Guide**; payload `dict.*` só no **Data Dictionary**.
